metadata.name: World Changers # Unrevealed Image
metadata.description: Meet the World Changers from the class of 2050. World Changers is a collection of 10,000 diverse kids living on the Ethereum blockchain. Support their future, help foster curiosity, hard work and excitement in this ambitious bunch destined to change the world. Over 50% of total mint is being donated to help fund schools, foundations and education-focused charities.
